Simple django module with two kind of custom fields.

These are not supposed to be used in production, are personal
experiments about customize Django's stuffs and buildout mess.

In order to test all this mess you can use the following commands:

 $ python bootstrap.py
 $ ./bin/buildout
 $ ./bin/test

TROUBLESHOOTING
---------------

If this error pops out

	Getting distribution for 'psycopg2'.
	Error: pg_config executable not found.

	Please add the directory containing pg_config to the PATH
	or specify the full executable path with the option:

	    python setup.py build_ext --pg-config /path/to/pg_config build ...

	    or with the pg_config option in 'setup.cfg'.

Simply do

 # apt-get install libpq-dev python-dev
